node.text: I got Progress on my Mind
The After affect of Holidays 🐡 +3 kilo
Merry Christmas everyone🎄 it’s the little things in life 🙌
You may be Taller but I’m always going to be the Older Brother 😆
I value these moments of being home because these are the people who built me into the Man I am today. Grateful for you all always humbling me and keeping me grounded🔨
Here come the Cookies and endless Carbs 🍪🎄
